{"tid":1532137,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"███ 萬眾期待！！！三國殺國戰交流區！！！███","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:33:06.000Z","uid":316655,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bf83f7662788f9460bc4d3a751427eb0d07f9101","tid":1532137,"uid":316655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三國殺 - 國戰<br />\n<br />\n絕對喺世界上最難玩嘅卡牌遊戲！！</span></span></strong></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢講求嘅唔單止喺你對遊戲嘅熟悉程度，仲包括捉摸對手心理同判斷力。呢啲都喺同你哋嘅生活息息相關！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家好，我係三國殺教授。適逢今年係三國殺OL十周年，而大家對國戰嘅了解肯定冇身份局咁深。所以教授我好希望集思廣益，將國戰嘅精髓傳揚開去，等更多人認識呢個咁好玩又咁難玩嘅模式！！！<br />\n<br />\n由今日開始，我會每日喺呢度發帖，由淺入深，一開始會先講下遊戲規則、卡牌設計等等，等大家有基本了解之後，就會逐步逐步教大家點樣憑住種種技巧戰勝對手！！<br />\n<br />\n無論喺新玩家定喺舊玩家，我保證只要你哋每日追post，你會好似發現新大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我講多次，因為呢個唔喺一般嘅遊戲！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsaW2Qe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsaW2Qe.jpg&h=c8c6c054&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05c076b532d9d5b6ec9800d5b684aad39bda8cf1","tid":1532137,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:27:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推到江永祥仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲有幾個鐘就返學啦好緊張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a0f5458714e490eb934a1c24f959332856df1d7","tid":1532137,"uid":205756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"係電腦到玩定真人"},{"pid":"97776b637caf0f8fb5c18b992e123df938d17f69","tid":1532137,"